translated: Åkerblom, Lennart Sigfrid, dentist, Gothenburg, born on April 1, 1883 in Örgryte, Gothenburg and Bohus County, eldest son of customs officer Johan L. Å. and Amelie Neukammer. Married on January 24, 19xx to Maud Lamm. Completed higher secondary education in Gothenburg in 1904, graduated with a degree in dentistry in 1906, became a licensed dentist in 1908. Employed as a clerk at the Customs Office in Gothenburg in 1904 and 1906, practiced dentistry in Gothenburg since 1908.
